this projet name Navy is a little game which played enter two terminals.

Exemple using :
./navy position/pos1.txt (is the 1st player)
my_pid: 4242
waiting for enemy connection...

./navy 4242 position/pos2 (is the 2nd player)
my_pid: 4250
successfully connected

if the 1st player has connected he display : enemy connected

after, the game begining and is at the 1st player to play

my positions:
 |A B C D E F G H
-+---------------
1|. . 2 . . . . .
2|. . 2 . . . . .
3|. . . . . . . .
4|. . . 3 3 3 . .
5|. 4 . . . . . .
6|. 4 . . . . . .
7|. 4 . 5 5 5 5 5
8|. 4 . . . . . .

enemy’s positions:
 |A B C D E F G H
-+---------------
